{"text_id":235538,"tokens":["The"," authors"," propose"," an"," approach"," to"," recommend"," products"," based"," on"," their"," textual"," descriptions"," as"," well"," as"," visual"," features"," of"," product"," images",".","\n","They"," use"," deep"," learning"," techniques"," for"," this"," purpose",".","  ","The"," main"," idea"," is"," that"," they"," represent"," each"," image"," with"," its"," corresponding"," text"," using"," content","2","vec"," (","a"," variant"," of"," word","2","vec",")"," which"," captures"," both"," semantic"," similarities"," between"," texts","/","images"," but"," also"," syntactic"," relationships"," within"," them","."," ","\n","This"," representation"," allows"," them"," to"," learn"," joint"," embeddings"," from"," these"," two"," modalities"," in"," order"," to"," predict"," user"," preferences"," over"," pairs"," of"," items",".","\n","I"," think"," it"," would"," be"," interesting"," if"," you"," could"," provide"," some"," more"," details"," about"," how"," exactly"," your"," model"," works","."," ","\n\n","In"," particular"," I"," am"," wondering"," whether"," there"," are"," any"," other"," approaches"," besides"," content","2","vec"," used","?"," Yes","  ","-"," we"," compare"," our"," results"," against"," several"," base","lines"," including"," Word","2","Vec"],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"bloomz","label":1}